              "fill": "$text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 900,
              "content": "Developers build intuitions about clean code — dependency injection, factories, middleware, deep directory trees, convention-over-configuration. For humans, these patterns reduce cognitive load. For LLMs, every single one is a trap. Each pattern hides information the LLM needs to generate correct code.",
